<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>VMoptions on B9F1</title><link>https://b9f1.com/tags/vmoptions/</link><description>Recent content in VMoptions on B9F1</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://b9f1.com/tags/vmoptions/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>IntelliJ 메모리 설정</title><link>https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/cover.png" alt="Featured image of post IntelliJ 메모리 설정" />&lt;h2 id="개요">📌개요
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>IntelliJ IDEA에서 메모리 힙 사이즈에 대해 전역 설정과 애플리케이션 별로 설정하는 방법을 알아본다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="내용">📌내용
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="전역-메모리-설정">전역 메모리 설정
&lt;/h3>&lt;h4 id="change-memory-settings">Change Memory Settings
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>&lt;code>Help &amp;gt; Change Memory Settings&lt;/code> 선택 → 팝업에서 힙 사이즈 변경&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-1.png"
width="1388"
height="995"
srcset="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-1_hu_6f84b7c7dbeeca5c.png 480w, https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-1_hu_eb4451e5584df4e2.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="IntelliJ"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="139"
data-flex-basis="334px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-2.png"
width="1385"
height="918"
srcset="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-2_hu_31916ff654233040.png 480w, https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-2_hu_a7e1562e26b713d8.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="IntelliJ"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="150"
data-flex-basis="362px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="edit-custom-vm-options">Edit Custom VM Options
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>IDE 메뉴에서 설정하는 방법도 있지만, 직접 설정 파일을 수정하는 방법도 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>Help &amp;gt; Edit Custom VM Options&lt;/code> 선택,
또는 각 설정 파일 경로를 찾아가서 수정하는 방법이 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Windows: &lt;code>%USERPROFILE%\AppData\Roaming\JetBrains\&amp;lt;IntelliJ 버전&amp;gt;\idea64.exe.vmoptions&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>macOS: &lt;code>~/Library/Application Support/JetBrains/&amp;lt;IntelliJ 버전&amp;gt;/idea.vmoptions&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Linux: &lt;code>~/.config/JetBrains/&amp;lt;IntelliJ 버전&amp;gt;/idea64.vmoptions&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-3.png"
width="1384"
height="917"
srcset="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-3_hu_d2715ae34a9bd5eb.png 480w, https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-3_hu_82773ad3ee9229e4.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="IntelliJ"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="150"
data-flex-basis="362px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"># 초기 힙 사이즈(최소 메모리)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">-Xms512m
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"># 최대 힙 사이즈 (권장: 시스템 메모리의 1/4 ~ 1/2)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">-Xms2048m
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>파일 수정 후 IntelliJ를 재시작하여 변경 사항을 적용한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="실행-프로필-별로-메모리-설정">실행 프로필 별로 메모리 설정
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>&lt;code>Run/Debug Configurations&lt;/code>에서 &lt;code>VM Options&lt;/code> 설정으로 특정 프로젝트의 애플리케이션을 실행할 때 사용되는 JVM의 메모리를 설정할 수 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>상단 툴바에서 &lt;code>Edit Configurations&lt;/code> 선택, 또는 &lt;code>Shift + Alt + F10&lt;/code> → &lt;code>Edit Configurations&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-4.png"
width="1384"
height="917"
srcset="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-4_hu_979f101c1146a18e.png 480w, https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-4_hu_94929ebb32c3f5d3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="IntelliJ"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="150"
data-flex-basis="362px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>VM options에 메모리 설정 추가&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">-Xms256m -Xmx1024m // 최소 256MB, 최대 1GB 할당
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://b9f1.com/p/2025-04-06-intelij-changing-the-memory-size/image-5.png"
width="1384"
height="1069"
